<hr data-start=3D"1759" data-end=3D"1762">
<h2 data-section-id=3D"k8ovjq" data-start=3D"1764" data-end=3D"1778">Explan=
ation</h2>
<p data-start=3D"1780" data-end=3D"1858">Hierarchical clustering creates a =
tree-like structure called a <strong data-start=3D"1843" data-end=3D"1857">=
dendrogram</strong>.</p>
<h3 data-section-id=3D"1fpn6yr" data-start=3D"1860" data-end=3D"1878">1. Si=
ngle Link</h3>
<ul data-start=3D"1879" data-end=3D"2018">
<li data-section-id=3D"s2k8mo" data-start=3D"1879" data-end=3D"1920">
<p data-start=3D"1881" data-end=3D"1920">Uses minimum distance between clus=
ters.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id=3D"y6glff" data-start=3D"1921" data-end=3D"1954">
<p data-start=3D"1923" data-end=3D"1954">Forms long chain-like clusters.</p=
>
</li>
<li data-section-id=3D"172a9t7" data-start=3D"1955" data-end=3D"1989">
<p data-start=3D"1957" data-end=3D"1989">Sensitive to noise and outliers.</=
p>
</li>
<li data-section-id=3D"8oimlu" data-start=3D"1990" data-end=3D"2018">
<p data-start=3D"1992" data-end=3D"2018">Lower clustering accuracy.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id=3D"ngaz3n" data-start=3D"2020" data-end=3D"2040">2. Com=
plete Link</h3>
<ul data-start=3D"2041" data-end=3D"2168">
<li data-section-id=3D"1lgducu" data-start=3D"2041" data-end=3D"2082">
<p data-start=3D"2043" data-end=3D"2082">Uses maximum distance between clus=
ters.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id=3D"1xbalok" data-start=3D"2083" data-end=3D"2130">
<p data-start=3D"2085" data-end=3D"2130">Produces compact and well-separate=
d clusters.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id=3D"19rsuhc" data-start=3D"2131" data-end=3D"2168">
<p data-start=3D"2133" data-end=3D"2168">Better matches actual wine classes=
.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id=3D"1gxrr3b" data-start=3D"2170" data-end=3D"2190">3. Gr=
oup Average</h3>
<ul data-start=3D"2191" data-end=3D"2334">
<li data-section-id=3D"1pn8qoy" data-start=3D"2191" data-end=3D"2234">
<p data-start=3D"2193" data-end=3D"2234">Uses average distance between all =
points.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id=3D"x4n1uo" data-start=3D"2235" data-end=3D"2263">
<p data-start=3D"2237" data-end=3D"2263">Gives balanced clustering.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id=3D"czxxvz" data-start=3D"2264" data-end=3D"2334">
<p data-start=3D"2266" data-end=3D"2334">Accuracy better than single link, =
slightly lower than complete link.</p>
</li>
</ul>
